WINSORISATION\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\b\fs22 \cf2 OBJECTIVE
\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs20 \cf0 Composite indicators can be sensitive to outliers in data. This tab gives the option to treat outliers using Winsorisation.  Where indicators may have outliers, the COIN Tool successively winsorises outlying points until the skew and kurtosis fall within the thresholds supplied in the 
\b Statistics tab
\b0 , up to a maximum of 5 winsorised points per indicator. The resulting treated data is displayed here, and can be optionally used or not in the 
\b TreatedData tab
\b0 .\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

