\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs20 \cf0 1) 
\b0 Select the winsorisation method (drop-down menu).\

\b 2) 
\b0 Enter the maximum number of indicators to be winsorised (up to 5), using the Skewness and kurtosis thresholds defined in the 
\b Statistics tab
\b0 .\
\
